feed.title: Bitcoin Core 0.9.2 release candidate 1 is available

entry.title: Bitcoin Core 0.9.2 release candidate 1 is available
entry.summary: Bitcoin Core version 0.9.2rc1 has been released as a minor version release, bringing bug fixes and some minor improvements. The release is available for download from the Bitcoin website. Additionally, new translations from Transifex have been added, and thanks were given to those who submitted translations.
